          "description": "Wonderful service!! We needed to find a resource that could give my disabled, housebound husband vaccinations. Jon from Downtown Pharmacy was great - prompt, communicative, friendly and courteous - I 100 percent recommend them to anyone needing in-home service!",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tJd2RGbzBTRkUyZFUxeVFtY3dhMFZRZDBSUlNIYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xbf5446b77f8652!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOkIwdFo0SFE2dU1yQmcwa0VQd0RRSHc%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "6 months ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2025-12-08T15:46:06+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "Christopher",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "111433034885536639066",
          "user_review_count": 3,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIW0bd6hQQrHPD_kch3pV0qLiobTfoDZTKtNKFR9n6y_Osfng=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "By far one of the best old school pharmacies in Manhattan insofar as treatment of their patients like family with new school like technology, they make everything from insurance to delivery to your home seamless.\nThere have been times where they have delivered to my home. Multiple times a day, not only my pharmaceuticals but also medical supplies. They have a wonderful selection. And they can get anything in within 24 hours. Do yourself a favor. Ever skip the line at those big impersonal, national pharmacies and do your business with downtown. You won't be sorry. We've used them for the past three years.And We are going to be customers for life.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2poeFQyRTVhbTFRZFhKeFYzSm5ZMVF5TFVKQmQzYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xbf5446b77f8652!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOjhxT2E5am1QdXJxV3JnY1QyLUJBd3c%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "7 months ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2025-11-21T16:16:57+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "Paola Corcoran",
          "rating": 1,
          "contributor_id": "111835842513868441911",
          "user_review_count": 9,
          "user_photo_count": 3,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLGQX8_8BLx4-8_Li1ZHlJ9O3qMizwhPUxGsMic5huHcvLjZg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "Quite surprised with unprofessionalism and unhelpful behavior displayed by the pharmacy staff. I've had multiple instances where questions for the pharmacy were met with unprofessionalism. No matter how polite and succinct the communication to pharmacy staff is framed, I am always met with disdain. Never experienced that in other pharmacies in the city, including ones not part of a chain (i.e. CVS). Will rather go to Tribeca Apothecary and even HealthSource Pharmacy uptown to get better service.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25wM05GRldPVUpIVTBKSlZHZExXUzFPT0hKRlRXYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xbf5446b77f8652!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOnp3NFFWOUJHU0JJVGdLWS1OOHJFTWc%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "10 months ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2025-08-25T13:11:28+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "Julian",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "106720058194955467029",
          "user_review_count": 62,
          "user_photo_count": 543,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYy68-kYiiBa-YEGLJoQf0696WGhnTEiHgrkGc5cyIM45kPFh0hQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "Really great pharmacy as they have 50\u00a2 chip bags and etc. however, many of the drinks and big chip bags are overpriced as I recall a bottle of Gatorade being $2.75 when I could get it from the Indian cart for $1",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21wMWFua3lTRlY2TjFaWlpUSkRlRlkyVW1ScFUyYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xbf5446b77f8652!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOmp1ankySFV6N1ZZZTJDeFY2UmRpU2c%7C%7C?hl=en",
